Enhancement: add more status counters to `restic copy`

`restic copy` now produces in JSON or text format status counters like the
`restic backup` command. Some fields do not make sense in the copy environment,
so the have been left to show a 0 count or size.

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/5175
https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/5319
